This paper focuses on text classification, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and falls under the computer science category of "Computation and Language" (cs.CL). The paper also utilizes statistical features and machine learning techniques, which are common in the sub-categories of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG), "Information Retrieval" (cs.IR), "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI), and "Neural and Evolutionary Computing" (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL, followed by cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, and cs.NE.
